| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2026-1462 — Recovery Inhibition (dragonforce)"
| comment "Status: stable | Level: high | ID: 2b7d2908-2e41-5d35-b3d5-c1548dcf1c6d"
